[] - User can create, read, update and delete a post

Interface
- User can view post form
- User can submit post form 
- User can edit post 
- User can delete post

User class
- attributes => name, password
- user signs up/logs in 
- has many posts

User Controller and Views
- '/users/signup' => renders sign up form
- '/users/signup' => processes sign up form, creates user, posts
- '/users/login' => renders login form
- '/users/login' => processes login form, post
- need to set sessions
- user can view their posts, '/users/:id/posts 

Posts class
- attributes => date, name, category....
- post belongs to a user

Post Controller and Views
- '/posts/new' => renders new post form 
- '/posts' => submits post
- '/posts' => renders all posts
- '/posts/:id => renders one instance
- '/posts/:id/:edit => renders update form for an instance
- '/posts/:id => updates instance 
- '/posts/:id/:delete => deletes instance 


where to start?
- set up classes
- set up database
- user controller
- posts controller 



